full_text: @TAIHistory needs #Texas #Authors Support. Please donate to help us stay in biz! COVID19 & Inflation have cut off our funding and we are barely holding on. You can send donations in any amount via https://t.co/eKXhQN4jW9 Thank you! https://t.co/MIpphUq21d
